            "family": {
                "name": "Terror Bird",
                "type": "monster_family",
                "sections": [
                    {
                        "name": "Diatryma",
                        "type": "section",
                        "text": "Diatrymas are 1st-level creatures akin to terror birds with a weak adjustment. These smaller kin of terror birds sport dark feathers and stand around 6 to 7 feet tall\u2014smaller than terror birds but no less ferocious. Diatrymas are mostly found in drier regions and sport small, orange beaks.",
